an> <span data-ttu-id="1d2a9-107">例如，在下列情況下引發事件：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1d2a9-107">For example, an event is raised under the following circumstances:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="1d2a9-108">您按一下設計介面上的區域。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1d2a9-108">You click a region on the design surface.</span></span>  
  
